696
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:10,140
We found

697
00:38:10,190 --> 00:38:11,070
her remains in a sinkhole

698
00:38:11,510 --> 00:38:13,100
on Mt. Fengdu.

699
00:38:18,830 --> 00:38:20,250
In this news article,

700
00:38:20,590 --> 00:38:21,940
