706
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,460
Back then,

707
00:38:45,740 --> 00:38:46,700
it was indeed Chang Feng

708
00:38:46,700 --> 00:38:47,750
who served as our guide.

709
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:49,910
His sister also came along.

710
00:38:50,710 --> 00:38:51,340
Yes.

